Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.84,0:00:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.04,0:00:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.65,0:00:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角 追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.15,0:00:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.60,0:00:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.68,0:00:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.91,0:00:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.42,0:01:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.36,0:01:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.37,0:01:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.94,0:01:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S．A．C．2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.61,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個狀況 你怎麼看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我原來估計的還要快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙也不是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該知道事情的嚴重性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以警察的反恐怖行動來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.43,0:02:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來才是最耗時間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.31,0:02:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#01再起動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人準備潛入電子腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每個人要先設定好清除竊聽程序的防壁哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離現在23分鐘前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝備各式槍支的犯罪集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.10,0:03:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,估領了位於這棟大樓46樓的中國大使館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前雖然還不清楚有多少名人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是可以確定事件發生當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.05,0:03:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少有十名以上的職員還留在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.32,0:03:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖份子的人數也一樣不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說能否用來當作掌握他們人數的參考還有疑問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們在犯罪聲明上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.59,0:03:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稱呼自己的組織為「個別的11人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算死守在大使館內嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.77,0:03:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來 9課的無限期待命指今也許能夠解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.47,0:03:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動命令正式下達之前都還很難說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.68,0:03:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這個「個別的11人」提出了什麼要求?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.35,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻廢除收容亞洲難民的政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及完全關閉散佈於國內各地共計五處的招慰難民居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都不是馬上做得到的要求啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是不是在開玩笑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中國政府為了避免要去收容大量出現的亞洲難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立了到出島的定期航線(出島位於日本九州島長崎市)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.07,0:04:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以這次才會遭到池魚之殃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果從正常的角度思考的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 在還沒有掌握他們真正的想法之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以亂下結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川 準備的怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大樓內的設備都裝上了竊聽裝置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轄區警方的情報呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.88,0:04:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了報導管制之外好像還啟動了大範圍干擾電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對無線通訊會有妨礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電子腦通訊裏面也混有雜音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使館內的攝影機全部完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.69,0:04:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在犯人只使用不含影像線路的電話線來跟警方聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.93,0:04:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 在那上面架設竊聽線路後回偽裝車這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達預定地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.18,0:04:46.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,映像簾：通電後會根據振動產生干擾\N使紅外線視覺器與激光竊聽器等外部監視全部失效的防護玻璃窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.18,0:04:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大樓的窗戶被映像簾蓋住無法確認裏面的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先設法中和窗簾的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的人待命準備攻堅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等待課長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是課長無法說服上面的長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就撤守對大樓的監視任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到脫衣酒吧去喝悶酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題出在發生這次恐怖攻擊的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨著招慰難民政策特別處理法的廢止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近政府準備在施政報告中提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.84,0:05:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無限期停止收容不斷涌入的難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,及分階段縮小難民居住區的政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.95,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在可以說是戰後首次針對難民做出重大政策轉變的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.69,0:05:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何都要避免輿論傾向於認定政府是向恐怖活動屈服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此有必要在犯人的要求洩漏給媒體之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎮壓住這次的恐怖活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我被叫來這裏的理由也在於此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.68,0:05:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳言說你非常精明好像是真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒必要花時間說奉承話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的狀況必須迅速處理才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就直說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.09,0:06:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以在下次國家審議會當中提出申請重建公安9課的預算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 鎮壓這次恐怖活動必須不犧牲任何一個人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.80,0:06:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是絕對條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.84,0:06:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要您下達攻堅命令我們隨時可以實現給您看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.64,0:06:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 荒卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.08,0:06:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說在正以最快速度跟相關單位聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.38,0:06:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他們簽署特殊部隊法案的修法檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在才要去製作檔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您認為還有這麼充裕的時間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.82,0:06:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有申請就出勤部隊 即使成功完成作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也絕對會成為媒體攻擊的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離9課那場解散大戲也還沒過多長時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.93,0:06:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臨時修法的許可申請如果沒有受理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就沒有你們出場的餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.77,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可惜 正如內務大臣所說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在檔到齊之前請繼續待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼動靜都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這種舉棋不定的內閣當對手連我們都想去當恐怖份子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.43,0:07:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在本廳也管不著的地方擅自出動的無照武裝集團...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果光看外在狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這樣就已經是百分之百的恐怖份子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過還真是諷刺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.51,0:07:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取代人稱藥島政權的前政權上台執政的茅葺內閣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.82,0:07:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是與以往戰後民族主義路線相反的反動保守政權嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在首相就職演說的公開承諾中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.82,0:07:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分階段停止難民政策應該也有包括在內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算默默在旁邊看跟他們這次要求相近的政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不也能付諸實施嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然戰後復興的期間正需要難民廉價的勞動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是國內失業率逐年增加 稅率也一直居高不下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上辛苦繳的這些稅有部分浪費在只出不進的難民政策上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,綜合現況也就不難理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何出現這些不耐煩的危險份子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家為了在國際社會上裝好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.19,0:08:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在難民援助問題上做條件交換可是負責收容難民的代價
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後還是由納稅人來承擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.56,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一部分難民實質上也是納稅人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 話雖然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在卻開始流傳一種觀念認為課重稅是要去幫助那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能搶走自己工作機會的傢伙過生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.41,0:08:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過直接就聯想到搞恐怖活動還真是跳躍式思考啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要這麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這些早就被強制解散的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次一發生警察處理不了的事件就被召集起來的這件事本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得也夠跳躍式思考了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在課長應該正憋著內心那股炸翻天的怒氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.06,0:09:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟新政權的大人物們見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過只有內務大臣留任不必引咎辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這工作真是不好幹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說在內務省本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.51,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下折衝國內各省廳的功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒換掉這位大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證明各方勢力都不認為他有威脅性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.98,0:09:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然以往這也是9課偽裝自己的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.06,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 這次任務要是順利完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們課裏要增加幾個新人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.06,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽過這件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我來說或許不太適合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.70,0:09:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過很難想像現在還有誰能跟得上9課的任務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.68,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正這事得等到這次任務按計劃執行完畢之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.32,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 雖然中和掉影像窗廉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是又被百葉窗擋住視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙似乎相當遵守作戰理論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.76,0:09:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在架好竊聽線路的電話在線開一條支線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.23,0:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要借用裏面那些傢伙的眼睛盡可能掌握狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了 交給我來辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 上鉤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.52,0:10:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.65,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事 不過很奇怪不是警察打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟敢派出斥候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來他們想把談判的時間提前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通訊中斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總共有九個同夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶頭的是哪個傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙除了做過電子腦化其它都是肉身嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正在開會哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛接到大使館那邊的聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.68,0:12:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方的攻堅部對跟恐怖份子發生衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方好像都有人受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.99,0:12:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該還沒有准許開火才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.63,0:12:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說是為了獲取裏面的情報才意外發生槍戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更糟糕的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一名警官成了人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:13:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖份子宣稱如果不在一小時內正式發表願意接受要求的公告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就殺了警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.61,0:13:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來每十分鐘處決一個人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.25,0:13:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們這樣做毫無益處只是讓事情更加惡化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事態已經是分秒必爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.82,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說在正需要您臨機應變做出判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.59,0:13:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對媒體的報導管制應該也撐不了多久了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.79,0:13:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是如游擊部隊一般的地方網絡上有人開始發表文章的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這次作戰就沒有意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.93,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文件還沒有準備齊全嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼您覺得這樣思考如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的恐怖活動從頭到尾都只靠警察攻堅就解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要不破壞這個故事大綱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.62,0:13:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理自己不就可以立刻下達攻堅命令了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.89,0:13:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會躲在警方作戰行動的後面秘密執行任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.36,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 還是要請總理在這段時間備齊讓我們的行動正當化的文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.24,0:14:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我可以保證  不過萬一你們鎮壓恐怖份子失敗的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我敢保證一定成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.78,0:14:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過除了請您相信我們之外沒有其它方法可以證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果您怎麼都無法下定決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.65,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也可以把公安9課今後的行動全當成我個人的獨斷專行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要把我一個人送去審判事情就可以解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.43,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算輿論想追究政府的責任應該也不會有人知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.58,0:14:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內務大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.55,0:14:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想請您用最快的速度聯絡警視廳長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有動靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.62,0:15:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在算起十五分鐘後SWAT將開始攻堅進入大使館內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前搶先潛入大使館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.43,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕那些恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得已的情形下准許開搶射殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.30,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救出人質是最優先考慮的事項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻堅的人選由你決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十五分鐘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.44,0:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們等了那麼久卻說的這麼輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤 先把直升機開回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就像大家剛剛聽到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內部的狀況如眼前所示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖份子有九名 其中一名已經死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.96,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先把建築物的構造和相對位置牢牢記在腦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰所需時間最長十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到SWAT攻堅之前的時間之所以會那麼短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人給我想成那是課長非常信賴我們的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻堅的人選呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.59,0:16:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特和托古薩帕茲和齋藤兩人一組進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.06,0:16:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用和SWAT不同的路線潛入大使館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搭電梯光明正大的進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.53,0:16:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們先出發我這邊準備好之後就過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.54,0:16:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十五分鐘後攻堅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面的情況都還沒搞清楚上面的到底想幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它的攻堅路線在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屋頂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有逃生梯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把一半人質移到逃生梯那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的一群人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.01,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人負責指揮卻還是能夠完成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是沒有組織性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這傢伙明明沒有什麼了不起的防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.25,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻找不到關於這個團體的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.93,0:17:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 我們現在要進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.19,0:17:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡可能靠近 引發他們自己內亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.23,0:17:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後一槍一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不可以打到人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我站好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電梯在動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.58,0:17:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看著人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你搞什...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特 有一個你沒打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提早開始攻堅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你給我過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 同伴...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 攻堅提前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 SWAT真是礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.57,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算我們在這裏倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其它個別的自我也會繼承我們的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.08,0:20:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以對我們來說死是沒有意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請你去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在窗戶外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.24,0:20:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的事 你們做的真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.58,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們將全面接受你們申請的預算 並准許重建以及經營部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.89,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是指揮攻堅行動的隊長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.92,0:21:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連一句挖苦的話都沒說真不像是課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為對象是女性?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.76,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該責罵的對象不是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.33,0:21:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況我也沒聽說過挖苦的話 說到嘴邊再吞下去會吃壞肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有這種上司不是很麻煩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種人一定會在自己養的狗脖子上套項圈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.28,0:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,況且以這次的攻堅命令來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.65,0:21:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很難說她不是避開自己的責任引導課長提出最佳的解決辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.02,0:21:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來她的確不只是聯合執政黨推出來的花瓶而已
